The ``django-ldapdb`` project is operated and maintained by:

* Jeremy Lainé <jeremy.laine@m4x.org> (https://github.com/jlaine), primary author
* Raphaël Barrois <raphael.barrois+django-ldapdb@polytechnique.org> (https://github.com/rbarrois)


